PrecisAcceptance of the transfer from the Province of Ontario of the administration and control over a parcel of waterfront land situate in the TOWN OF MEAFORD, which contains an area of some 15.979 hectares, which is to be used to accommodate a breakwater and to provide a basin for a small craft harbour and marina.
